d></c02><c02 id="aspace_868719226dc82c7fb752a0bf9293f4de" level="file"><did><unittitle>1 Small Journal of Accounts (Investments, Bonds and Stocks) n.d.</unittitle><container id="aspace_fe4ea6027b2625679ed93e527c9cafb9" label="Mixed Materials [31924064716081]" type="box">7-6-13 1</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_a23b68f1427442f5cf429cf298905cc7" level="file"><did><unittitle>Account book,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1911/1913" type="inclusive">1911-1913</unitdate><container id="aspace_8a207a6111aeca46ab79d26a9746d84f" label="Mixed Materials [31924064692035]" type="volume">7-6-13 1</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_b059427377c7861a2b95515c51f8c748"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Listing all the expenses of the various departments of the University from <date>May 1911</date> to <date>Mar. 1914</date>. The listings are by departments and identify the appropriation from which each sum was taken.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_961db1094f9ebc55080dd748931811bb" level="file"><did><unittitle>Records of Bonds,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1880/1914" type="inclusive">1880-1914</unitdate><container id="aspace_5c4e715b182555cd0e3ebd7ed53a6708" label="Mixed Materials [31924064692050]" type="volume">7-6-13 2</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_9c19163e61800dc14c1c919122dc43bd"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>A listing of university held bonds from <date>Oct. 30, 1880</date> through <date>June 27, 1914</date>. Lists issuing company, type of bond, number issue date, date and place payable, interest payable and principal.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_4ae5f048c8d36795337ea5e6f1a5f439" level="file"><did><unittitle>Records of interest payments on mortgages,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1900/1915" type="inclusive">1900-1915</unitdate><container id="aspace_50ee0e9e1efb95456b6ebaa26e239d80" label="Mixed Materials [31924064692068]" type="volume">7-6-13 3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_4411c0b7505b9d8a833325d62a399c49" level="file"><did><unittitle>Records of mortgages,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1876/1915" type="inclusive">1876-1915</unitdate><container id="aspace_8526eda09c6be3b588af6b3039f8d15e" label="Mixed Materials [31924064692043]" type="volume">7-6-13 4</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_37cb8cf1168c6053761d49b90caa822a"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Mortgages book giving complete data on mortgages held by the university from <date>1876</date> to <date>1915</date>. Lists purchase data, mortgagee amount of cash involved, interest rate and date. Also from whom purchased if purchased, and where recorded and where payable.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_958683993b529c3b28094e373c61f6dc" level="file"><did><unittitle>Record of interest payments on bonds,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1900/1915" type="inclusive">1900-1915</unitdate><container id="aspace_ca6a13f8015c0902b8ca8afa432adf92" label="Mixed Materials [31924064723004]" type="volume">7-6-13 5</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_f7e4dae993ce0de6d2bdd03871ba4538" level="file"><did><unittitle>Index of Mortgages,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce">n.d.</unitdate><container id="aspace_ec40f7eb6a84179453a3a067f22e65ea" label="Mixed Materials [31924065439808]" type="volume">7-6-13 6</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_8bfc466d943ae212fa88a713624eaea7"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Index to university mortgage books. No dates. Gives name of mortgage and page number in the entire book.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_52c3a34a82fc5419c8a3ba0f9c921b1b" level="file"><did><unittitle>Record of Bonds, 1880-1931 ; also, Record of mortgages</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1880/1931" type="inclusive">1880-1931</unitdate><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1876/1900" type="inclusive">1876-1900</unitdate><container id="aspace_1066e1e42d801cb8bf2299b1452deef7" label="Mixed Materials [31924065087573]" type="volume">7-6-13 7</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_52c3d650f8b9ff0f3e786f270480130f"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>List of mortgages financed by the university from <date>Apr. 10, 1876</date> to <date>Jan. 4, 1900</date>. Back of volume contains same listing for bonds from <date>May 8, 1880</date> to <date>Jan. 12, 1900</date>. This book lists complete information on both bonds and mortgages.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_d460f7beff691d60afd0865f3fab6e97" level="file"><did><unittitle>Index (?)</unittitle><container id="aspace_66a85bf53c9fa2cabb2a4c1a08d59f9e" label="Mixed Materials [31924065439790]" type="volume">7-6-13 8</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_7f45f12863023b4020523d6a4be415e9" level="file"><did><unittitle>Index of Mortgages,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce">n.d.</unitdate><container id="aspace_25304b6e618872bfa111403b0d778397" label="Mixed Materials [31924065439782]" type="volume">7-6-13 9</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_4d17dbea34fe1c056e4fede27f51f361"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Mortgage and bond book listing the various persons against whom mortgages and bonds were held. It contains an index and all listings are alphabetically arranged along with the folio numbers and amount of cash involved. There are no dates.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_8eb86367e8669d9519bd1ff7933bb1cf" level="file"><did><unittitle>Record of Securities,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1872/1890" type="inclusive">1872-1890</unitdate><container id="aspace_dcbc5489d57c1fe274689d2829d595bb" label="Mixed Materials [31924065087565]" type="volume">7-6-13 10</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_199f6c090becda0fc8b690642322dea5"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>A listing of the securities in which the university endowment funds were invested. Listed are the purchased date, firm, type of security, number of security, date issued, when payable, amount of interest.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_8c453dc1434a05483423a068c3c4e514" level="file"><did><unittitle>Cash book (outgoing),</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1897/1913" type="inclusive">1897-1913</unitdate><container id="aspace_8373f23a4db942e368a07951063ad7cd" label="Mixed Materials [31924064692019]" type="volume">7-6-13 11</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_2fe75eaa01b51a4ff68610b780b7fa45"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Day book listing daily payments from <date>Aug. 6, 1899</date> to <date>Feb. 1913</date>. Entries are intermittently placed throughout the book.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_5fe862ed6a3e8a10e41a7eaf18319012" level="file"><did><unittitle>Index of Securities</unittitle><container id="aspace_d53a6c1b9773339f481f2d406fa5b6d5" label="Mixed Materials [31924064723038]" type="volume">7-6-13 12</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_ffc37f5684e494b6b25e7e9a9ce83792" level="file"><did><unittitle>C.U. Appropriation book,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1900/1920" type="inclusive">1900-1920</unitdate><container id="aspace_a0932ec7bd3b4f06472d9cdcefe16f6c" label="Mixed Materials [31924064723012]" type="volume">7-6-13 13</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_5a635eb9f7620beb453d860402a212c8"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>University appropriations book <date>1900-1920</date>. Lists two years to a page, moneys appropriated for university expenses by department. Lists amount of appropriation, expenditure and balance of appropriation left after each entry.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_f7ad9ca2c958e1fa3e21443c70ac2d1c" level="file"><did><unittitle>C.U. Reports, 1864-1868 (Removed - see Acc. 47-1-1527)</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1864/1868" type="inclusive">1864-1868</unitdate><container id="aspace_e4cede74394a1537a71a8a93326f544a" label="Mixed Materials" type="volume">7-6-13 14</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_4e3120ed4a5b452a4f31b52c97ff83ad" level="file"><did><unittitle>Records of Special Funds,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1879/1885" type="inclusive">1879-1885</unitdate><container id="aspace_9a8d231dd56ebf8ec56785c5b2c8ad7f" label="Mixed Materials [31924064723020]" type="volume">7-6-13 15</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_e08ab7c7962e0ea31ea8c45bfdb72ffa"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>University ledger listing: 1) University land script fund, 2) University endowment, 3) Various university funds. These entries cover the dates, <date>Feb. 1879</date> to <date>June 1885</date> by month and by separate fund.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_58c439d44bf00e9eb77b89fccc54fa2f" level="file"><did><unittitle>General Ledger A,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1868/1871" type="inclusive">1868-1871</unitdate><container id="aspace_11193ed9de19dff11a87b25b8fd14319" label="Mixed Materials [31924064692076]" type="volume">7-6-13 16</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_7c7dd66345861a891939c959bb572337"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Ledger listing the various expenses in an itemized form which the various departments of the university and persons concerned with the university incurred from <date>Nov. 25, 1868</date> to <date>Aug. 31, 1871</date>. Contains an index.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_5e3c2ee69f99133a49c9b04e9d12a15f" level="file"><did><unittitle>College of Forestry - Voucher Records,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1899/1914" type="inclusive">1899-1914</unitdate><container id="aspace_99228691e7dbed8d4f9dc1a93773db7b" label="Mixed Materials [31924065444378]" type="volume">7-6-13 17</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_e3ab6fa07d97ede9a8ae9794c7f94dbd"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Voucher record-College Forest Appropriation Book. Sixty pages of voucher listings by number from 1 to 780. Dates extend from <date>May 20, 1899</date> to <date>Apr. 22, 1914</date>. Each entry describes the person date the sum concerned was appropriated and total of the full appropriation from which the sum was taken.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_26127ca652afe5589371bf1f5de1e192" level="file"><did><unittitle>College of Forestry - Voucher Record,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1898/1903" type="inclusive">1898-1903</unitdate><container id="aspace_877bfc59b44b106bd25dbd3563357741" label="Mixed Materials [31924065444360]" type="volume">7-6-13 18</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_11769a62223b1d5f035d6d2aa140f780"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Voucher Record-College Forest Appropriations. Lists date, amount of bill paid and total amount of appropriation from which money was taken. <date>May 12, 1898</date> to <date>Oct. 17, 1903</date>.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_cc0c9abb33c03fdd0f3a31dda5c69343" level="file"><did><unittitle>Professional Pension Recod,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1903/1944" type="inclusive">1903-1944</unitdate><container id="aspace_54c7416bb0ff694b45c75a94ed390bee" label="Mixed Materials [31924065076915]" type="volume">7-6-13 19</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_311df06ffa6164383b5dde826ea8cefe"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Account book listing professional pension fund payments, by professors name from <date>1903</date> to <date>1947</date>. Index of back cover.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_a7fcba3774648c9a3a7da9dcc5c232ae" level="file"><did><unittitle>Student Loan Fund,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1873/1904" type="inclusive">1873-1904</unitdate><container id="aspace_08eba7d76c789b619b60147ee229971b" label="Mixed Materials [31924065440475]" type="volume">7-6-13 20</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_c2be9721e3917e0b21ad524d41a059ce"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Student Loan Fund book. Students and sums are listed by name from <date>1873-1904</date>.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_53fd2180ae64ed251835b29c8bb61cd4" level="file"><did><unittitle>Record of Sage College Room Rents,</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1895/1900" type="inclusive">1895-1900</unitdate><container id="aspace_34d5f2b9769e2dad15c207c9ddc9dc94" label="Mixed Materials [31924065457677]" type="volume">7-6-13 21</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_2a026b3338727221f99578bb88d564f6"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Sage College Record of Room Rent <date>1895-1900</date>. Listings are made by person, monthly.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_5da3b35b801836e86d188cc49aa0ed86" level="file"><did><unittitle>Abstracts of Ithaca property owned by Ezra Cornell and Cornell University</unittitle><container id="aspace_00f372710b5cd025f70dc0373f7bd1b9" label="Mixed Materials [31924065087557]" type="volume">7-6-13 22</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_6fa038b24fd415be849f80a2815927a2"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Seventy-three pages of titles, abstracts, maps and descriptions of various land in and about Ithaca which were transferred through Ezra Cornell to the university. These abstracts have record of land as early as <date>1822</date> and extend up to <date>1867</date>. The various mortgages on the land are also described.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 id="aspace_de041d6dcc64e0a85e83848d5034b79e" level="file"><did><unittitle>Account Book (Day Book),</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce">1886-1871</unitdate><container id="aspace_f89280e3a3149ffe5577a2c57a9af16d" label="Mixed Materials [31924065439204]" type="volume">7-6-13 23</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_642375203848a6fc7b86de56194384db" level="file"><did><unittitle>Account Book (Day Book),</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1871/1879" type="inclusive">1871-1879</unitdate><container id="aspace_39f6279af6d3f35a8d82634379ec8438" label="Mixed Materials [31924065439774]" type="volume">7-6-13